{"type":null,"faqId":43848,"title":"蓝牙中所用到的各个功能，各是用的什么协议？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">华为手机中运用到的蓝牙协议及各个匹配的功能如下：HFP（打电话）、HSP（打电话）、A2DP（听音乐）、AVRCP（音乐播放控制）、OPP（蓝牙文件传输）、PBAP（联系人同步）、MAP（短信同步）、HID（使用蓝牙键盘鼠标）、PAN（蓝牙共享网络）、BLE（连接蓝牙低功耗设备如手环等）。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9349","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442399557000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10","visitedTimes":4,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"蓝牙,协议","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}